.TH "__audit_sockaddr" 9 "__audit_sockaddr" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
__audit_sockaddr \- record audit data for sys_bind, sys_connect, sys_sendto
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" __audit_sockaddr
.BI "(int len "  ","
.BI "void *a "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "len" 12
data length in user space
.IP "a" 12
data address in kernel space
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns 0 for success or NULL context or < 0 on error.
